      "    Bin scores into N equal-width bins on [0, 100].",
      "    MI_b = Σ_(bin,label) P(bin,label) · log2(P(bin,label) / (P(bin)·P(label)))",
      "    w_b  = MI_b / Σ MI_*",
      "",
      "Higher MI → bucket carries more information about the label.",
